English band Morcheeba are coming to Cape Town and will play a show at Kirstenbosch Gardens on Friday, 6 April. General admission for the concert costs R495 per person and tickets can be bought on Friday 19 January. The band have toured the world for the last two decades and have sold millions of albums. Some of their biggest hits include: Rome Wasn't Built in a Day ; Enjoy the Ride and Gimme Your Love . Source: Channel24 Music